These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
7 different games are played: bridge, chess, whist, scrabble, monopoly, snooker, poker
City: nizza, prague, colone, liverpool, berlin, marseilles, london
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles, traveling, writing, board-games, video-games, camping
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to nizza##2
 4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 6. the person playing bridge is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person playing monopoly##2
 8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
10. the person playing poker is the person traveling to colone##1
11. the person traveling to marseilles is the person playing scrabble##1
12. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing whist##1
13. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person traveling to berlin##1
14. the person playing snooker is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Game   | monopoly | bridge     | snooker | chess | scrabble | poker  | whist  |
| City   | nizza  | liverpool        | prague  | london     | marseilles   | colone       | berlin   |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | camping | writing    | traveling  | board-games | video-games | skydiving |

