.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, snooker, canasta, poker, scrabble, domino
There are 7 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lavender, yellow, coral, light-blue, azure, blood-red
7 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, snake, goat, hedgehog, lizard, rat
 1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 2. the person who likes light-blue is the person who likes light-blue##1
 3. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 4. the person who likes coral is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is the person playing domino##1
 6. the person playing mah-jongg is the owner of the goat##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person who likes blood-red and the owner of the rat##2
 8. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
10. the person playing snooker is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
12. the owner of the ferret is the person playing bridge##1
13. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
14. the person playing canasta is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
15. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
16. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Game   | scrabble | domino      | canasta     | mah-jongg  | poker | snooker | bridge |
